{"data":[{"name":"107:1","price":"1. Tahukah kamu (orang) yang mendustakan agama?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6198,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"107:2","price":"2. Maka itulah orang yang menghardik anak yatim,","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6199,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"107:3","price":"3. dan tidak mendorong memberi makan orang miskin.","arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6200,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"107:4","price":"4. Maka celakalah orang yang salat,","arabic":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6201,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"107:5","price":"5. (yaitu) orang-orang yang lalai terhadap salatnya,*(927)","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَن صَلَاتِهِمۡ سَاهُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6202,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*927). Orang-orang yang tidak menghargai serta melalaikan pelaksanaan dan waktu-waktu salat.","lang":"id"},{"name":"107:6","price":"6. yang berbuat riya’,","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ يُرَآءُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6203,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*928). Riya` ialah melakukan perbuatan tidak untuk mencari keridaan Allah, melainkan untuk mencari pujian atau kemasyhuran di masyarakat.","lang":"id"},{"name":"107:7","price":"7. dan enggan (memberikan) bantuan.*(929)","arabic":"وَيَمۡنَعُونَ ٱلۡمَاعُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6204,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"*929). Sebagian mufassir mengartikan dengan “enggan membayar zakat”.","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un","Chapter Al-Ma'un","Ma'un","Surah Ma'un","Chapter Ma'un","Al Ma'un","Surah Al Ma'un","Chapter Al Ma'un","Surah 107","Chapter 107","The Small Kindnesses","الماعون"]}